This is sample project from 'Quick Start' chapter of the 'MinGW Starter'
book (ISBN 5626).

The project contains next files:

main.cpp - C++ source file with main function
resource.rc - file with Windows Controls configuration
resource.h - header for binding resource identifiers and C++ code
Makefile - GNU Make utility rules file to build project

All these files are described detailed in the book.

This is command to build the project:

$ make
